*ruby-1.6.8-r4 (11 Dec 2003)

  11 Dec 2003; Mamoru KOMACHI <usata@gentoo.org> ruby-1.6.8-r3.ebuild,
  ruby-1.6.8-r4.ebuild, ruby-1.8.0-r1.ebuild, ruby-1.8.0-r2.ebuild,
